      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I got it! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. You won\u2019t find a single flaw on this beauty; it\u2019s basically like buying a brand-new car. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
