    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically superlative, having undergone documented rod bearing replacement and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gate engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures linear power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension has been meticulously maintained with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the car's legendary handling dynamics. With zero VANOS rattle and a flawless factory finish, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically optimized icon of the analog era.",
